photographs of the Department of State.\n                        Where can I find them?\n\nWhat is Foreign Relations of the United\n                        States?\n\nI would like to purchase a FRUS volume. How can I\n                        do so?\n\nWhat formats are FRUS volumes available\n                        in?\n\nWhen will the FRUS volume on \u2026 be\n                        published?\n\nDo I need to request permission to quote from a FRUS volume?\n\n\n\nAbout the Office of the Historian\n\nHow can I get a job in the Office of the Historian?\n\nDoes the Office of the Historian offer internships?\n\nCan I receive updates on activities at the Office of the Historian?\n\n\n\nDepartment History\n\nWhy is the Department called the Department of State?\n\nWhy does the Department of State have possession of the Great Seal of the\n                        United States?\n\n\n\nDiplomatic Relations\n\nWhen did the United States start/break off relations with \u2026?\n\nWhat country was the first to recognize the United States?\n\nWho was the first U.S. Consul?\n\nWhen was the first U.S. treaty signed?\n\nWhat was the first U.S. treaty with a non-European nation?\n\nWhat was the first U.S. treaty to be ratified under the\n                        Constitution?\n\nWhen and where was the first U.S. consular post established?\n\n\n\nThe Secretaries of State\n\nHow many Secretaries of State have there been?\n\nHas any member of the Foreign Service served as Secretary of State?\n\nWho was the first woman to serve as Secretary of State?\n\nWho was the first African American to serve as Secretary of State?\n\nWere there equivalents to the Secretary of State prior to the\n                        Constitution?\n\nWho was the first Secretary of State to travel outside the United States\n                        while in office?\n\nWho was the first Secretary of State to travel outside the United States\n                        on official business?\n\n\n\nAmbassadors and Chiefs of Mission\n\nWho was the first Ambassador to \u2026?\n\nWho were the first U.S. Ambassadors?\n\nHow many U.S. Ambassadors have been killed by militants?\n\n\n\nThe Foreign Service\n\nWhat was the origin of the Foreign Service?\n\nWhen was the Consular Service established?\n\nWhen did U.S. consuls first receive a salary?\n\nWho were the first professional consular appointees?\n\nWhat was the forerunner of the Foreign Service Examination?\n\nWhen was the present-day Foreign Service established?\n\n\n\nWomen in the Foreign Service\n\nAfrican Americans in the Foreign Service\n\nDiplomatic and Consular Posts, 1781-2010\n\nDepartment Personnel, 1781-2010\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nAbout\n\n\nContact Us\n\nFrequently Asked Questions\n\nThe Historian\n\nHistorical Advisory Committee\n\nRecent Publications\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nLearn more\nHome\n\nSearch\n\nFAQ\n\n\n\nTopics\nHistorical Documents\n\nDepartment History\n\nCountries\n\nMilestones of U.S. Foreign Relations\n\n\n\nContact\nAbout Us\n\nContact Us\n\n\n\nImprint\nPrivacy Notice\n\nExternal Link Policy\n\nCopyright Info\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nOffice of the Historian, Bureau of Public AffairsUnited States Department of State\n\nhistory@state.gov\n\nPhone: 202-955-0200\nFax: 202-955-0268\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n          var _gaq = _gaq || [];\n          _gaq.push(['_setAccount', 'UA-23344799-1']);\n          _gaq.push(['_setDomainName', 'history.state.gov']);\n          _gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);\n\n          (function() {{\n              var ga = document.createElement('script'); ga.type = 'text/javascript'; ga.async = true;\n              ga.src = ('https:' == document.location.protocol ? 'https://ssl' : 'http://www') + '.google-analytics.com/ga.js';\n              var s = document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0]; s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga, s);\n          }})();\n        \n\n"}
